Hi , we’re just two idiots with too much time on our hands these quotes are things we hear in our public school or that we say

summary:
*Hope and Scott are sitting outside, hank is drinking a margarita, baby ants have invaded the cup* 
Luis : are they swimming?...
body:
*Hope and Scott are sitting outside, hank is drinking a margarita, baby ants have invaded the cup*

Luis : are they swimming?

Hank, sweetly: no, they’ve committed suicide.

This quote was from a sweet old lady that was talking to her grandson while they were at a cookout and @nonbinaryandtired overheard this !!!!
